query:
INSERT INTO username_proofs (
                fid,
                username,
                timestamp,
                type,
                signature,
                owner,
                deleted_at
            )
            VALUES ($1, $2, $3, $4, $5, $6, $7)
            ON CONFLICT (username, fid) DO UPDATE SET
                deleted_at = CASE
                    WHEN $7 IS NOT NULL THEN $7
                    ELSE username_proofs.deleted_at
                END
